name: pyhdf
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.9.0" %}

package:
    name: pyhdf
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: pyhdf-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: http://hdfeos.org/software/pyhdf/pyhdf-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: c20c58e53f8fbdc47a1fcdec954262528f486cfcb4efa7e1c2e8847ad3e8092f

build:
    number: 1

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
        - numpy x.x
        - jpeg 9*
        - zlib 1.2*
        - hdf4
    run:
        - python
        - numpy x.x
        - jpeg 9*
        - zlib 1.2*
        - hdf4

test:
    imports:
        - pyhdf

about:
    home:  http://hdfeos.org/software/pyhdf
    license: Public Domain
    summary: Python interface to the NCSA HDF4 library

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
